<h3>Introduction</h3>
<p>
   Monkey project team, is proud to announce the availability of <i>Monkey HTTP Daemon 0.12.1</i>. This new release comes with minor fixes in charset encodings and fix
   a bug in dirlisting plugin:
</p>

<h3>What is new ?</h3>
<p>
<ul>
        <li>Fixed full support for UTF-8</li>
        <li>Hexadecimal to decimal converter: full rewrite</li>
        <li>Dirlisting Plugin: fix a crash when a broken symlink is found</li>
        <li>Dislisting Plugin: Guineo Theme now set UTF-8 charset encoding in HTML header</li>
</ul>
</p>

